<p class="courseblockdesc">
Examine the field of information security to prepare students for their future roles as business decision-makers.  Presents a balance of the managerial and technical aspects of information security.  Course Information:  3 undergraduate hours.  4 graduate hours.  Prerequisite(s):  <a href="/search/?P=IDS%20200" title="IDS&#160;200" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IDS 200');">IDS&#160;200</a> or the equivalent.<br />
