<p class="courseblockdesc">
Text mining for business applications. It will cover document representation, text categorization and clustering, basic natural language processing techniques, sentiment analysis, probabilistic topic models and text visualization. Course Information: 3 undergraduate hours. 4 graduate hours. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=IDS%20371" title="IDS&#160;371" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IDS 371');">IDS&#160;371</a> or consent of the instructor.<br />
