Prior and posterior distributions; conjugate priors; value of information; applications to decision making in business. Course Information: 3 undergraduate hours. 4 graduate hours. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=IDS%20371" title="IDS&#160;371" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IDS 371');">IDS&#160;371</a>.<br />
