<p class="courseblockdesc">
Technologies, applications and use of information systems in healthcare. Electronic health records and how healthcare data is organized by providers and payers. Applications of data analytics and machine learning in healthcare. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=IDS%20570" title="IDS&#160;570" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IDS 570');">IDS&#160;570</a> or equivalent. Knowledge of statistical software R, SAS, SPSS etc. Recommended background: A course in data mining: <a href="/search/?P=IDS%20472" title="IDS&#160;472" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IDS 472');">IDS&#160;472</a> or <a href="/search/?P=IDS%20572" title="IDS&#160;572" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IDS 572');">IDS&#160;572</a> or equivalent. Consent of instructor required for non-CBA students.<br />
